True.

00:02:45.899 --> 00:02:47.868
Though I must say,
I'm a little bit envious

00:02:47.868 --> 00:02:49.703
of their carefree attitude.

00:02:49.703 --> 00:02:51.471
Yeah, me too.

00:02:51.471 --> 00:02:54.041
Sometimes a nap's just
what the doctor ordered.

00:02:54.041 --> 00:02:56.276
Save your laziness
for another day.

00:02:56.276 --> 00:02:58.645
[screams]

00:02:58.645 --> 00:03:02.482
That showcase the Twerpette's
entering, I'm entering too.

00:03:02.482 --> 00:03:04.117
But this time I'll win.

00:03:04.117 --> 00:03:07.821
Oh, yes, daintily dancing
toward Kalos Queen.

00:03:07.821 --> 00:03:09.022
[groans]

