I'd rather take a nap.

00:03:14.394 --> 00:03:16.730
[EXCITED]

00:03:16.730 --> 00:03:17.931
[DELIGHTED]

00:03:17.931 --> 00:03:20.534
[PROUD]/[CRITICAL]

00:03:20.534 --> 00:03:22.035
[SURPRISED]/[ANNOYED]

00:03:22.035 --> 00:03:23.036
[WATER GUN MOVE]

00:03:23.036 --> 00:03:25.172
[EXCITED]

00:03:25.172 --> 00:03:28.275
[EAGER]

00:03:29.176 --> 00:03:31.344
[CARING]

00:03:31.344 --> 00:03:33.780
[CARING]

00:03:33.780 --> 00:03:37.250
They're gorgeous.
Thanks a lot, Braixen.

00:03:37.250 --> 00:03:39.786
Now just a second.

00:03:39.786 --> 00:03:41.421
It's perfect.

00:03:41.421 --> 00:03:43.256
You're so good at that.

00:03:43.256 --> 00:03:44.991
Thanks, I made one for you too.

00:03:44.991 --> 00:03:46.159
Sure.

00:03:46.159 --> 00:03:48.028
[gasps]

00:03:48.028 --> 00:03:50.063
[giggles]
So pretty.

00:03:50.063 --> 00:03:51.198
[EAGER]

00:03:51.198 --> 00:03:52.866
SERENA
'This is yours.'

00:03:52.866 --> 00:03:54.301
[CURIOUS]

00:03:54.301 --> 00:03:55.736
SERENA
'You're the cutest.'

00:03:55.736 --> 00:03:57.404
[EXCITED]/[SHOCKED]

00:03:57.404 --> 00:03:59.940
[STRUGGLING]/[PAINED]

00:03:59.940 --> 00:04:02.142
[DETERMINED]

00:04:02.142 --> 00:04:04.711
[CARING]/[GRATEFUL]

00:04:04.711 --> 00:04:06.179
[SURPRISED]

00:04:06.179 --> 00:04:07.447
You okay?

00:04:07.447 --> 00:04:09.549
[CURIOUS]

00:04:17.157 --> 00:04:18.925
It's an Eevee.

00:04:22.796 --> 00:04:24.931
POKEDEX
Eevee. The Evolution Pokémon.

00:04:24.931 --> 00:04:28.168
Eevee is rarely seen and can
adapt to severe habitats

00:04:28.168 --> 00:04:31.571
by evolving, changing
its capabilities and form.

00:04:31.571 --> 00:04:33.006
Eevee's so cute.

00:04:33.006 --> 00:04:35.275
Eevee obviously likes to dance.

00:04:35.275 --> 00:04:36.877
It's so light on its feet.

00:04:36.877 --> 00:04:40.213
ASH 'Serena.
Clemont says the tea's ready.'

00:04:40.213 --> 00:04:42.783
Huh? Eevee, wait.

00:04:42.783 --> 00:04:43.984
BONNIE
'Aw.'

00:04:43.984 --> 00:04:45.919
It ran away.

00:04:47.621 --> 00:04:50.157
We're coming, Ash.

00:04:50.157 --> 00:04:52.225
BRAIXEN
[DISAPPOINTED]

00:04:54.494 --> 00:04:56.930
You really saw a dancing Eevee?

00:04:56.930 --> 00:04:59.733
Yeah, and it moved
so beautifully.

00:04:59.733 --> 00:05:01.902
Just like it was dancing on air.

00:05:01.902 --> 00:05:05.205
Wow, what do you know.
Sorry I scared it.

00:05:05.205 --> 00:05:07.607
I felt like
when I watched Eevee dancing

00:05:07.607 --> 00:05:10.243
'I might be able to come up
with a brand‐new routine.'

00:05:10.243 --> 00:05:11.611
[STRUGGLING]

00:05:11.611 --> 00:05:14.548
So let's have it show you
its dance moves again.

00:05:14.548 --> 00:05:15.782
[EXCITED]

00:05:15.782 --> 00:05:17.017
Yeah. You should.

00:05:17.017 --> 00:05:19.186
[EXCITED]

00:05:19.186 --> 00:05:21.922
This time, you should
try not to scare it away.

00:05:21.922 --> 00:05:23.523
You're right about that.

00:05:23.523 --> 00:05:24.858
[ENTHUSIASTIC]

00:05:24.858 --> 00:05:26.593
Okay. Eevee, here we come.

00:05:26.593 --> 00:05:28.028
[EXCITED]

00:05:28.929 --> 00:05:31.665
That Eevee's unbelievable.

00:05:31.665 --> 00:05:33.667
It's the ultimate Pokémon

00:05:33.667 --> 00:05:36.069
for an even more
elegant performance.

00:05:36.069 --> 00:05:39.606
Hey, don't forget about me.
I can cut a rug.

00:05:40.473 --> 00:05:42.409
♪ Put your right foot in ♪

00:05:42.409 --> 00:05:44.644
♪ And your left
and do it again ♪♪

00:05:44.644 --> 00:05:46.847
[whimpers]

00:05:49.249 --> 00:05:50.383
[AFFIRMATIVE]

00:05:51.284 --> 00:05:52.819
Wonder where Eevee is.

00:05:53.720 --> 00:05:54.955
[CURIOUS]

00:05:54.955 --> 00:05:57.524
I'm sure Eevee must live
somewhere around here

00:05:57.524 --> 00:05:58.558
but where?

00:05:58.558 --> 00:06:00.260
[giggles]

00:06:00.260 --> 00:06:02.662
The future is now,
thanks to science.

00:06:02.662 --> 00:06:04.598
CLEMONT
'Clemontic Gear, on.'

00:06:04.598 --> 00:06:06.766
I thought that we'd
encounter a situation

00:06:06.766 --> 00:06:08.335
precisely like this one.

00:06:08.335 --> 00:06:10.937
It's a robotic radar
that detects living things.

00:06:10.937 --> 00:06:13.206
My "Living Thing Finder
Mark Two."

00:06:13.206 --> 00:06:14.975
‐ "Mark Two?"
‐ That's correct.

00:06:14.975 --> 00:06:17.277
I once used it
to search for you.

00:06:17.277 --> 00:06:19.312
The living organism
detection power

00:06:19.312 --> 00:06:21.781
used to be my
invention's weakest point.

00:06:21.781 --> 00:06:23.316
But it's been improved.

00:06:23.316 --> 00:06:26.052
It can now detect
any living thing.

00:06:26.052 --> 00:06:27.654
Science is so amazing.

00:06:27.654 --> 00:06:29.990
Okay. We're counting on you.

00:06:29.990 --> 00:06:32.659
Our target is very small.

00:06:32.659 --> 00:06:36.162
CLEMONT 'So let's narrow
the search down to its size.'

00:06:36.162 --> 00:06:37.631
Here we go.

00:06:38.398 --> 00:06:41.334
[whirring]

00:06:41.334 --> 00:06:44.371
‐ 'Found it.'
‐ Whoa. That was quick.

00:06:44.371 --> 00:06:46.339
And it's over there.

00:06:46.339 --> 00:06:47.807
[CALM]

00:06:47.807 --> 00:06:49.442
SERENA
'But that's a Vivillon.'

00:06:49.442 --> 00:06:51.444
Uh, one more time.

00:06:51.444 --> 00:06:52.479
whirr whirr whirr

00:06:52.479 --> 00:06:55.215
Found it for sure. There.

00:06:55.215 --> 00:06:58.118
BONNIE
'Eevee? Or not.'

00:06:58.118 --> 00:07:01.021
Okay, back to the drawing board.

00:07:01.021 --> 00:07:02.822
I don't understand.

00:07:02.822 --> 00:07:05.926
[Clemont whimpering]

00:07:08.228 --> 00:07:11.331
[screaming]

00:07:11.998 --> 00:07:14.167
[groaning]

00:07:14.167 --> 00:07:16.469
Oh, well. Better luck next time.

00:07:16.469 --> 00:07:19.239
Thanks.
I could use a little luck.

00:07:20.407 --> 00:07:22.575
Let's split up.
That'll be better.

00:07:22.575 --> 00:07:25.211
You're right.
So, we'll head over that way.

00:07:25.211 --> 00:07:27.781
Braixen? And Pancham?
You all set?

00:07:27.781 --> 00:07:29.316
[FOCUSED]/[ENTHUSIASTIC]

00:07:29.316 --> 00:07:31.017
Hey, Noibat? Talonflame?

00:07:31.017 --> 00:07:33.420
ASH 'Let me know
if you see anything.'

00:07:33.420 --> 00:07:35.755
[FOCUSED]

00:07:35.755 --> 00:07:37.123
Will you help too?

00:07:37.123 --> 00:07:38.758
[FOCUSED]/[ENTHUSIASTIC]

00:07:38.758 --> 00:07:40.794
Clemont? What about you?

00:07:40.794 --> 00:07:42.128
Alright.

00:07:42.128 --> 00:07:44.531
[EAGER]/[INTERESTED]

00:07:44.531 --> 00:07:45.532
ASH
'Eevee?'

00:07:45.532 --> 00:07:47.300
PIKACHU
[CALLING]

00:07:47.300 --> 00:07:48.969
HOPPIP
[STARTLED]

00:07:48.969 --> 00:07:50.103
TALONFLAME
[EAGER]

00:07:50.103 --> 00:07:53.106
PIDGEY
[SCARED]

00:07:53.106 --> 00:07:54.174
NOIBAT
[CURIOUS]

00:07:54.174 --> 00:07:55.475
SKIPLOOM
[CALM]

00:07:55.475 --> 00:07:57.944
CLEMONT
'Eevee, where are you?'

00:07:57.944 --> 00:07:59.446
ODDISH
[CALM]

00:07:59.446 --> 00:08:00.647
FROGADIER
[DISAPPOINTED]

00:08:02.549 --> 00:08:04.017
BONNIE
'Have you seen Eevee?'

00:08:04.017 --> 00:08:05.552
BURMY
[CALM]

00:08:05.552 --> 00:08:08.755
Eevee. Where are you?

00:08:08.755 --> 00:08:10.457
[EAGER]

00:08:10.457 --> 00:08:11.992
Braixen, any luck?

00:08:11.992 --> 00:08:13.793
[DISAPPOINTED]

00:08:13.793 --> 00:08:16.629
I see. Wow.
Maybe it isn't here.

00:08:16.629 --> 00:08:18.965
Braixen?
Let's try it one more time.

00:08:18.965 --> 00:08:20.000
[FOCUSED]

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:21.468
And you look over that way.

00:08:21.468 --> 00:08:22.635
[FOCUSED]

00:08:28.608 --> 00:08:30.543
Eevee.

00:08:32.445 --> 00:08:34.247
[PANICKED]/[URGENT]

00:08:34.247 --> 00:08:35.315
Huh?

00:08:35.315 --> 00:08:37.083
[whines]

00:08:37.083 --> 00:08:38.852
[screams]

00:08:41.321 --> 00:08:42.322
Huh?

00:08:42.322 --> 00:08:45.492
Eevee. Wow, you saved me.

00:08:45.492 --> 00:08:48.395
[HESITANT]/[SCARED]

00:08:48.395 --> 00:08:49.729
Huh?

00:08:54.034 --> 00:08:55.902
[sighs]

00:08:55.902 --> 00:08:56.903
Huh?

00:08:56.903 --> 00:08:58.438
[laughs]

00:08:58.438 --> 00:09:00.607
SERENA
'I'll leave this for Eevee.'

00:09:02.075 --> 00:09:04.044
PANCHAM/BRAIXEN
[CALLING]/[CURIOUS]

00:09:04.044 --> 00:09:07.380
No. Not yet. Let's go.

00:09:19.426 --> 00:09:21.394
I wonder
if this will really work.

00:09:21.394 --> 00:09:23.363
Serena makes yummy Poké Puffs.

00:09:23.363 --> 00:09:25.799
I'm sure Eevee will love them.

00:09:26.900 --> 00:09:29.335
Back off, Chespin.
That's not for you.

00:09:29.335 --> 00:09:30.336
Mm‐hmm.

00:09:30.336 --> 00:09:31.738
[CALM]

00:09:31.738 --> 00:09:32.839
[leaves rustling]

00:09:32.839 --> 00:09:34.507
[EXASPERATED]

00:09:34.507 --> 00:09:36.009
[SURPRISED]

00:09:36.910 --> 00:09:38.812
[FRIENDLY]

00:09:43.716 --> 00:09:46.119
[SNEAKY]

00:09:46.119 --> 00:09:48.021
Oh, no.

00:09:48.021 --> 00:09:49.856
The Poké Puff's gone.

00:09:49.856 --> 00:09:51.491
Huh?

00:09:51.491 --> 00:09:53.026
[grunting]

00:09:53.026 --> 00:09:54.027
I knew it.

00:09:54.027 --> 00:09:56.529
[DEFENSIVE]

00:09:56.529 --> 00:09:59.632
[URGENT]

00:10:01.000 --> 00:10:03.703
ASH/SELENA/BONNIE/CLEMONT
Who's that Pokémon?

00:10:08.441 --> 00:10:11.411
ASH/SELENA/BONNIE/CLEMONT
It's Eevee.

00:10:11.411 --> 00:10:13.713
[APPEARING]

00:10:17.317 --> 00:10:19.285
You saw Eevee for real?

00:10:19.285 --> 00:10:22.522
Yeah. But sadly, it ran away.

00:10:22.522 --> 00:10:23.890
BONNIE
'Too bad.'

00:10:23.890 --> 00:10:25.592
ASH 'Let's look for it
again tomorrow.'

00:10:25.592 --> 00:10:27.861
CLEMONT
'Good idea.'

00:10:38.204 --> 00:10:40.607
[SURPRISED]

00:10:40.607 --> 00:10:42.375
[CURIOUS]

00:10:42.375 --> 00:10:44.878
[DELIGHTED]

00:10:48.882 --> 00:10:51.985
[snoring]

00:11:02.462 --> 00:11:03.863
[CONCERNED]

00:11:03.863 --> 00:11:05.465
Shh.

00:11:10.336 --> 00:11:12.272
[STARTLED]

00:11:13.406 --> 00:11:15.508
[CONCERNED]

00:11:15.508 --> 00:11:17.143
I didn't mean to wake you up.

00:11:17.143 --> 00:11:19.546
I couldn't sleep, that's all.

00:11:19.546 --> 00:11:21.614
I'm going to take a walk.

00:11:30.056 --> 00:11:31.157
[gasps]

00:11:45.471 --> 00:11:47.740
[CURIOUS]

00:11:47.740 --> 00:11:49.509
Look what it's wearing.

00:11:49.509 --> 00:11:51.244
SERENA
'Eevee likes it.'

00:11:56.449 --> 00:12:00.153
Wow, I'd really like to become
great friends with that Eevee.

00:12:00.153 --> 00:12:02.789
Do you two think it would be
a good idea if I did?

00:12:02.789 --> 00:12:04.324
[HAPPY]

00:12:04.324 --> 00:12:06.292
[ENCOURAGING]

00:12:06.292 --> 00:12:08.061
Thanks. I will.

00:12:08.061 --> 00:12:10.396
But how in the world
am I ever going to let

00:12:10.396 --> 00:12:12.932
Eevee know
that I wanna be friends?

00:12:23.843 --> 00:12:27.180
Now, let's find Eevee
today for sure.

00:12:27.180 --> 00:12:28.514
You know what?

00:12:28.514 --> 00:12:31.251
I don't think I want to look for
Evee the same way today.

00:12:31.251 --> 00:12:33.419
[gasps]

00:12:33.419 --> 00:12:35.255
You're not giving up, are you?

00:12:35.255 --> 00:12:38.324
No way. I've got a better idea.

00:12:41.894 --> 00:12:43.696
ASH
'What are you gonna do?'

00:12:43.696 --> 00:12:45.565
I figure it would be
better if we show

00:12:45.565 --> 00:12:47.767
Eevee our performance instead.

00:12:47.767 --> 00:12:49.769
Really? Your performance?

00:12:49.769 --> 00:12:51.537
SERENA
'Right. It makes sense.'

00:12:51.537 --> 00:12:54.507
We were drawn to how happy
Eevee looked while dancing

00:12:54.507 --> 00:12:57.143
so I think it would be
a great idea to show

00:12:57.143 --> 00:12:59.445
Eevee how happy
we are by dancing too.

00:12:59.445 --> 00:13:00.980
Great. I like it.

00:13:00.980 --> 00:13:04.550
After all, your performances
are really good.

00:13:04.550 --> 00:13:06.786
Bonnie, that is so sweet.

00:13:06.786 --> 00:13:09.756
So what do you two say?
Are we on?

00:13:09.756 --> 00:13:11.858
[FOCUSED]

00:13:14.027 --> 00:13:15.795
Braixen, Flamethrower.

00:13:15.795 --> 00:13:18.898
[FLAMETHROWER MOVE]

00:13:19.365 --> 00:13:21.534
[gasps]

00:13:21.534 --> 00:13:22.869
[SURPRISED]

00:13:25.104 --> 00:13:26.439
[CURIOUS]

00:13:27.340 --> 00:13:30.076
Okay, Pancham, Dark Pulse, go.

00:13:30.076 --> 00:13:31.344
[EXCITED]

00:13:31.344 --> 00:13:33.446
[DARK PULSE MOVE]

00:13:34.514 --> 00:13:36.282
Ta aa.

00:13:44.957 --> 00:13:46.592
[PROUD]

00:13:47.727 --> 00:13:50.363
‐ Amazing.
‐ It sure was.

00:13:50.363 --> 00:13:51.564
[IMPRESSED]

00:13:51.564 --> 00:13:53.132
[giggles]

00:13:53.132 --> 00:13:54.801
Huh?

00:13:54.801 --> 00:13:56.769
So did you like what we did?

00:13:56.769 --> 00:13:58.371
Not too bad, right?

00:13:58.371 --> 00:14:00.106
‐ Huh?
‐ Huh?

00:14:00.106 --> 00:14:01.874
[SURPRISED][SCARED]

00:14:04.510 --> 00:14:05.678
It's Eevee.

00:14:05.678 --> 00:14:07.680
Eevee was this close
the whole time?

00:14:07.680 --> 00:14:10.016
How cool is that? It worked.

00:14:10.016 --> 00:14:12.151
Eevee came, just like you
thought it would.

00:14:12.151 --> 00:14:14.487
Mm‐hmm. See, Eevee.

00:14:14.487 --> 00:14:17.790
The three of us really like
to perform together as a team.

00:14:17.790 --> 00:14:20.793
We compete with other performers
in the Pokémon Showcase

00:14:20.793 --> 00:14:22.462
and it's a whole lot of fun.

00:14:22.462 --> 00:14:24.731
[ENCOURAGING]

00:14:24.731 --> 00:14:26.833
SERENA 'Do you think maybe
you'd like to perform with us'

00:14:26.833 --> 00:14:29.235
'on stage
in the Pokémon Showcase?'

00:14:30.470 --> 00:14:31.971
That's a great idea.

00:14:31.971 --> 00:14:34.540
Then Eevee would get
to be part of your team.

00:14:35.508 --> 00:14:36.909
[SURPRISED]

00:14:36.909 --> 00:14:39.645
Because, it's so much fun
to watch you dance.

00:14:39.645 --> 00:14:42.582
I want lots more people
to see you too.

00:14:43.383 --> 00:14:44.550
What do you say?

00:14:44.550 --> 00:14:46.886
Would you like to be
part of our group?

00:14:55.094 --> 00:14:56.095
[SCARED]

00:14:56.095 --> 00:14:57.897
Eevee.

00:14:57.897 --> 00:14:59.766
Hey, what's going on?

00:14:59.766 --> 00:15:02.301
Prepare for trouble,
it's surely not you.

00:15:02.301 --> 00:15:04.737
And make it double,
we love what we do.

00:15:04.737 --> 00:15:07.106
To protect the world
from devastation.

00:15:07.106 --> 00:15:09.742
To unite all people
within our nation.

00:15:09.742 --> 00:15:12.512
To ruin your performance
at every turn.

00:15:12.512 --> 00:15:16.048
To extend our reach
with power to burn.

00:15:16.048 --> 00:15:18.484
‐ Jessie.
‐ And James.

00:15:18.484 --> 00:15:21.187
Team Rocket blasts off
at the speed of light.

00:15:21.187 --> 00:15:24.323
Surrender now or prepare
for a choreographed fight.

00:15:24.323 --> 00:15:25.858
Meowth, that's right.

00:15:25.858 --> 00:15:27.460
[AFFIRMATIVE]

00:15:28.995 --> 00:15:30.997
Team Rocket.
Not you guys again.

00:15:30.997 --> 00:15:33.299
[TERRIFIED]

00:15:33.299 --> 00:15:35.701
‐ You let Eevee go.
‐ 'What for?'

00:15:35.701 --> 00:15:39.338
I'm the one who's traveling down
the road to stardom with Eevee.

00:15:39.338 --> 00:15:41.741
‐ What do you mean?
‐ Bonnie, no.

00:15:41.741 --> 00:15:44.577
You heard him. Gourgeist, go.

00:15:45.778 --> 00:15:47.180
[APPEARING]

00:15:47.180 --> 00:15:49.549
Inkay, join the fray.

00:15:51.651 --> 00:15:52.885
[APPEARING]

00:15:52.885 --> 00:15:54.687
Inkay. Use Psybeam.

00:15:54.687 --> 00:15:56.389
[PSYBEAM MOVE]

00:15:56.389 --> 00:15:58.658
Pikachu, Electro Ball, go.

00:15:58.658 --> 00:16:01.828
[ELECTRO BALL MOVE]

00:16:04.030 --> 00:16:06.866
Alright, Braixen
and Pancham, help Eevee.

00:16:06.866 --> 00:16:08.201
[DETERMINED]

00:16:08.201 --> 00:16:09.602
[STRUGGLING]/[SURPRISED]

00:16:09.602 --> 00:16:13.239
She's such an irritating
Twerpette. Shadow Ball.

00:16:13.239 --> 00:16:14.373
[SHADOW BALL MOVE]

00:16:14.373 --> 00:16:15.975
Braixen, Flamethrower.

00:16:15.975 --> 00:16:19.078
[FLAMETHROWER MOVE]

00:16:20.213 --> 00:16:22.248
Okay, Inkay, use Tackle.

00:16:22.248 --> 00:16:23.416
[TACKLE MOVE]

00:16:23.416 --> 00:16:25.685
Quick, Pikachu, Iron Tail.

00:16:25.685 --> 00:16:27.987
[IRON TAIL MOVE]

00:16:27.987 --> 00:16:29.121
[EXERTION]

00:16:29.121 --> 00:16:30.389
Use Foul Play.

00:16:30.389 --> 00:16:32.825
[FOUL PLAY MOVE]/[PANICKED]

00:16:32.825 --> 00:16:33.826
[PAINED]

00:16:33.826 --> 00:16:34.927
No, Pikachu.

00:16:34.927 --> 00:16:37.530
Now, Pancham, use Stone Edge.

00:16:37.530 --> 00:16:39.799
[STONE EDGE MOVE]

00:16:40.633 --> 00:16:42.869
[screaming]

00:16:43.369 --> 00:16:44.570
[PANICKED]

00:16:44.570 --> 00:16:46.138
Eevee.

00:16:46.138 --> 00:16:49.141
You keep that Twerpette
away from Eevee.

00:16:49.141 --> 00:16:51.244
Seed Bomb, now.

00:16:51.244 --> 00:16:52.245
[SEED BOMB MOVE]

00:16:52.245 --> 00:16:55.248
[panting]

00:16:55.248 --> 00:16:57.049
Eevee.

00:16:57.917 --> 00:16:58.918
[grunts]

00:16:58.918 --> 00:17:00.953
Serena.

00:17:00.953 --> 00:17:02.955
Are you okay?

00:17:02.955 --> 00:17:04.824
[SHOCKED]/[SCARED]

00:17:04.824 --> 00:17:07.426
‐ No you don't.
‐ Dance your way back here.

00:17:07.426 --> 00:17:10.496
You're wasting
your fancy footwork.

00:17:10.496 --> 00:17:11.831
That's far enough.

00:17:13.866 --> 00:17:15.167
Oh, please.

00:17:15.167 --> 00:17:17.303
Gourgeist, Seed Bomb.

00:17:17.303 --> 00:17:18.804
[SEED BOMB MOVE]

00:17:18.804 --> 00:17:20.273
[whines]

00:17:20.273 --> 00:17:21.274
Serena.

00:17:21.274 --> 00:17:23.175
[groaning]

00:17:23.175 --> 00:17:24.176
Huh?

00:17:24.176 --> 00:17:25.378
[PROTECT MOVE]

00:17:25.378 --> 00:17:26.979
BONNIE
'Eevee did that?'

00:17:26.979 --> 00:17:29.815
‐ It just used Protect.
‐ To help Serena

00:17:29.815 --> 00:17:32.351
[AMAZED]

00:17:32.351 --> 00:17:35.354
[SWIFT MOVE]

00:17:35.354 --> 00:17:36.856
[whimpering]

00:17:36.856 --> 00:17:39.158
Pikachu. Use Thunderbolt.

00:17:39.158 --> 00:17:40.927
[THUNDERBOLT MOVE]

00:17:40.927 --> 00:17:43.029
[screaming]

00:17:43.930 --> 00:17:46.265
Eevee was my path to stardom.

00:17:46.265 --> 00:17:48.134
Check out this fancy footwork.

00:17:48.134 --> 00:17:50.836
Actually, air travel
doesn't use feet.

00:17:50.836 --> 00:17:53.439
‐ We're blasting..
‐ Off again.

00:17:53.439 --> 00:17:56.542
GOURGEIST/WOBBUFFET
[PANICKED]

00:17:57.410 --> 00:17:59.111
Can't you take a hint?

00:17:59.111 --> 00:18:01.881
Eevee, thanks so much.

00:18:01.881 --> 00:18:04.016
[SURPRISED][HESITANT]

00:18:04.016 --> 00:18:05.885
So, as I was saying..

00:18:05.885 --> 00:18:07.119
Please, Eevee.

00:18:07.119 --> 00:18:09.221
Won't you travel along with us?

00:18:09.221 --> 00:18:11.991
If we all dance together,
it'll be more fun.

00:18:11.991 --> 00:18:14.360
[ENCOURAGING]

00:18:15.962 --> 00:18:17.463
[HESITANT]

00:18:24.537 --> 00:18:26.072
[AFFECTIONATE]

00:18:26.072 --> 00:18:27.873
So that means
you'll come with us?

00:18:27.873 --> 00:18:28.874
[HAPPY]

00:18:28.874 --> 00:18:30.076
Welcome aboard.

00:18:30.076 --> 00:18:32.545
[cheering]

00:18:35.548 --> 00:18:36.716
Ready?

00:18:46.792 --> 00:18:48.928
Ta‐da. Ah.

00:18:48.928 --> 00:18:52.298
A new chapter in my life,
because I caught an Eevee.

00:18:52.298 --> 00:18:54.634
[HAPPY]

00:18:54.634 --> 00:18:55.668
Yeah, good for you.

00:18:55.668 --> 00:18:56.936
[EXCITED]

00:18:56.936 --> 00:18:59.005
‐ You did it.
‐ Congratulations.

00:18:59.005 --> 00:19:00.673
Thanks, you guys.

00:19:00.673 --> 00:19:03.142
So come back out and say hi.

00:19:04.477 --> 00:19:07.580
[FRIENDLY]

00:19:08.781 --> 00:19:10.650
Okay gang, let's go.

00:19:10.650 --> 00:19:11.951
You too.

00:19:14.153 --> 00:19:17.256
[FOCUSED]

00:19:18.924 --> 00:19:21.027
[FOCUSED]

00:19:22.561 --> 00:19:24.196
It's nice to meet you.

00:19:24.196 --> 00:19:25.965
[FRIENDLY]

00:19:25.965 --> 00:19:26.966
Huh?

00:19:26.966 --> 00:19:30.670
[SURPRISED/[STARTLED]

00:19:30.670 --> 00:19:33.005
I'd say when Eevee gets
in front of others

00:19:33.005 --> 00:19:35.474
it feels just a little bit shy.

00:19:35.474 --> 00:19:37.309
Now don't you worry, Eevee.

00:19:37.309 --> 00:19:39.211
Everyone's real nice.

00:19:39.211 --> 00:19:41.514
So, let's be friends.

00:19:41.514 --> 00:19:43.549
[EAGER]/[STARTLED]

00:19:43.549 --> 00:19:44.583
Uh oh.

00:19:44.583 --> 00:19:47.153
[SCARED]

00:19:47.153 --> 00:19:50.256
[PROUD]/[SCARED]

00:19:51.257 --> 00:19:53.359
[FRIENDLY]/[STARTLED]

00:19:54.360 --> 00:19:55.628
[CONCERNED]/[HAPPY]

00:19:55.628 --> 00:19:57.730
[JEALOUS]

00:19:58.864 --> 00:20:00.700
[DEFENSIVE]

00:20:00.700 --> 00:20:03.602
Well, what do you know?
It's comfortable with Bunnelby.

00:20:03.602 --> 00:20:05.705
That's because Bunnelby's nice.

00:20:05.705 --> 00:20:06.739
[DEFENSIVE]

00:20:06.739 --> 00:20:09.842
[EAGER]/[SCARED]

00:20:10.876 --> 00:20:12.344
Hey. Cut it out.

00:20:12.344 --> 00:20:15.314
Hey Serena, I'm really glad
you made a new friend.

00:20:15.314 --> 00:20:16.415
Thanks.

00:20:17.116 --> 00:20:18.551
Me too.

00:20:18.551 --> 00:20:21.721
Braixen and Pancham.
And now Eevee.

00:20:21.721 --> 00:20:24.557
SERENA 'We will win
the Pokémon Showcase together.'

00:20:24.557 --> 00:20:26.592
ASH
'I'm gonna train hard too.'

00:20:26.592 --> 00:20:28.928
[laughing]

00:20:30.730 --> 00:20:32.198
[HAPPY]

00:20:34.700 --> 00:20:36.435
I'm so happy you're here.

00:20:36.435 --> 00:20:38.671
[HAPPY]

00:20:38.671 --> 00:20:41.006
NARRATOR There's no doubt that
things are going to get even

00:20:41.006 --> 00:20:44.243
livelier with Serena's new
friend Eevee in the group.

00:20:44.243 --> 00:20:48.080
So now, our heroes are off
once again to Anistar City

00:20:48.080 --> 00:20:50.850
as the journey continues.

